#8280
Welcome to Project Twilight~
Welcome to \tBProject Twilight\tn, a World of Darkness roleplaying MUD
set in the fictional city of Bal Harbor. This tutorial will walk you
through the basics of playing the game.

The \tCArchivist\tn is here to greet you. Each room ahead covers a
different topic with \tChighlighted commands\tn you can try.

Type '\tWlook sign\tn' to read the welcome sign, then go \tWnorth\tn
to begin the tutorial.
~
