sign~
Welcome to the Project Twilight Tutorial! This orientation will walk you through the basics of playing the game. Each room ahead covers a different topic with commands for you to try. Take your time - there is no rush. When you are finished, you will earn a small experience bonus for completing the tutorial. You can return here anytime by typing 'newbie'.~
