#8285
Tutorial: Commerce and Jobs~
Money makes the world go around, even in the World of Darkness:

  \tClist\tn - See what a shopkeeper has for sale
  \tCbuy\tn \tW<item>\tn - Purchase an item
  \tCsell\tn \tW<item>\tn - Sell an item to a shopkeeper
  \tCstocks\tn - View the stock market
  \tCtrade\tn \tW<buy/sell> <shares> <company>\tn - Trade stocks

Jobs provide income and experience. Find an employer and use
'\tCjob apply\tn' to get started. Type '\tCjob commands\tn' for
the full list.

Sal runs a small shop here. Try '\tWlist sal\tn' to see his wares,
then go \tWnorth\tn.
~
