E
combos~
Combat moves include strikes (lblow, rblow, kick, skick, bite), grabs (lgrab, rgrab), blocks (lblock, rblock, fblock), and movement (cflip, croll, cjump, spin, sweep). Chain them together for combo effects. Use cstop to disengage and cstand to rebalance.~
E
combat~
Project Twilight uses a combo-based combat system. Moves can be chained together for greater effect. Type 'help combos' for a complete list of moves and combinations. Remember: most conflicts are resolved through roleplay. The combat system is for situations where dice and mechanics are needed.~
