#8289
Tutorial: The Races of Bal Harbor~
Three supernatural races inhabit the World of Darkness, each with
unique abilities and a rich history:

  \tWHumans\tn - Mortals who may wield political power and numina.
    Organizations include Pentex, the FBI, and the Society of Leopold.
    Go \tCeast\tn for more.

  \tWWerewolves\tn - The Garou, defenders of Gaia, warriors of rage.
    Tribes include Bone Gnawers, Glass Walkers, Silent Striders, and
    Silver Fangs. Go \tCsouth\tn for more.

  \tWVampires\tn - The Kindred, undead predators of the night.
    Camarilla clans include Brujah, Gangrel, Malkavian, Nosferatu,
    Toreador, Tremere, and Ventrue. Go \tCwest\tn for more.

Or go \tWnorth\tn to skip ahead to the exit.
~
