#8290
Tutorial: Humans~
\tBHumans\tn may lack supernatural power, but they wield something
equally dangerous: \tCpolitical influence\tn.  

Humans can be \tCnominate\tnd and \tCvote\tnd into positions of office
including Judges, Aldermen, Mayor, and Police Chief.  The Mayor can
\tCappoint\tn a Police Chief.  

Human organizations grant unique abilities: 
  \tWPentex\tn - A megacorporation secretly serving dark forces.
  \tWFBI\tn - Federal agents investigating supernatural activity.  
  \tWSociety of Leopold\tn - Modern inheritors of the Inquisition.  

Each organization provides access to \tCnumina\tn, supernatural abilities
unique to awakened mortals.  

Go \tWnorth\tn to continue to the exit.  
~
