nominate~
Syntax: nominate <player> <position> - Nominate a mortal for a position of office. Only mortals can hold city positions. Use 'nominees' to see current candidates.~
E
vote~
Syntax: vote <player> <position> - Cast your vote for a candidate in a city election. Only mortals may vote, and you may only vote once per election.~
