#8291
Tutorial: Werewolves~
\tBThe Garou\tn are warriors of Gaia, shapeshifters born to defend
the natural world against the corruption of the Wyrm.

Key werewolf commands:
  \tCtransform\tn \tW<form>\tn - Shift between Human, Crinos, and Wolf
  \tCgifts\tn - View your supernatural gifts
  \tCuwalk\tn - Step sideways into the Umbra (spirit world)
  \tCrage\tn - Channel your fury for supernatural speed and strength

Available tribes:
  \tWBone Gnawers\tn - Urban scavengers and survivors
  \tWGlass Walkers\tn - Tech-savvy city wolves
  \tWSilent Striders\tn - Wandering messengers and scouts
  \tWSilver Fangs\tn - Noble rulers of Garou society

Go \tWnorth\tn to continue to the exit.
~
0 8 0
