XNUMB1~
Unnamed Room~
E
XDUMB1~
None~
E
rage~
Rage is the gift of Gaia to her warriors. It allows supernatural speed and strength, and fuels the transformation between forms. But beware - too much rage can lead to frenzy.~
E
uwalk~
Syntax: uwalk (also: sidestep) - Step sideways into the Umbra, the spirit realm. The Umbra is a mirror of the real world inhabited by spirits. Werewolves can traverse it naturally.~
E
gifts~
Syntax: gifts (or powers) - Shows your available supernatural gifts and their levels. Gifts are granted by your totem and can be advanced with experience.~
E
transform~
Syntax: transform <form> (also: shift, shapechange) - Changes your form between Human (homid), Crinos (war form), and Wolf. Each form has different strengths and limitations. See 'help crinos' and 'help wolf' for details.~
