Tutorial Complete~
\tBCongratulations!\tn You have completed the Project Twilight
tutorial. You now know the basics of movement, communication,
roleplaying, items, commerce, and your race's abilities.

\tYRemember:\tn
  * Type '\tChelp <topic>\tn' anytime for more information
  * Use '\tChelpline <message>\tn' to ask for help from other players
  * Type '\tCnewbie\tn' to return to this tutorial anytime
  * Type '\tCtips\tn' for helpful gameplay tips

When you are ready to enter the city, type '\tWstep City Center\tn'
to begin your adventure in Bal Harbor!

You can also go \tWsouth\tn to review the race information.
~
